# Server-side only. Loaded by the Vite file-bus middleware (via loadEnv) and used
# in Node. It is never exposed to the browser, because it has no VITE_ prefix.
#
# Copy this file to ".env.local" (gitignored) and fill in your token.
#
# GitHub personal access token (classic) with the "public_repo" scope.
# Lets the app read public repos and issues, and later fork and open PRs.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
